name: Text to image generator - getimg.ai Flux.1
description:
Generates an image from a text prompt using the getimg.ai API and Flux.1 model.

Image width and height from 256 to 1280 pixels (must be multiple of 8).

Format of the image can be jpeg or png (default is jpeg).

Number of denoising steps is from 1 to 6 (default is 4). More steps usually can produce higher quality images, but take more time to generate.
